Reasoning: The paper discusses an artificial visual system that learns to attend to regions of interest while solving a classification task. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the use of a fully recurrent neural network and reinforcement learning protocol suggests that the paper may also belong to the neural networks (cs.NE), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
